                ))}
              </ul>
              <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--gcs-muted); margin-top: 1rem;">Breakfast served 8 – 11. Lunch served 11 – 2. Free delivery the whole window.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

